extendedInfo.description: Become good with numbers. Practice makes perfect! Let's enjoy mental math and train your brain!Features- Times Table Training(1~99!)- Useful tips to simplify difficult math problems and exercises to use them.- Four arithmetic operations training in three difficulty levels- "Hide Question" mode to train to hold numbers in memory for mental calculation.- Flash mental calculationPlease let me know any bugs and suggestions, and your secrets of mental math!Keywordsmental math, mental calculation, mental arithmetic, multiplication tables, times table, brain training, math tricks, math workout, math exercise, math, arithmetic

reviews.comment: A great little app. Good for memorizing multiplication results if you\'ve forgotten them since school. Some good techniques on doing mental math in the tutorial section (i.e. 54x9 = 54x10-54).  I have no complaints at all about this software. I recommend it if you want to improve your mental calculation skills.

reviews.title: In the right direction
reviews.comment: This is definitely in the right direction and with a few improvements, it might be worth downloading.  As with a lot of apps, there are absolutely no instructions, and so you might sit there baffled for a few seconds over some of the features.  A really good subtraction module, but that was all I saw in the 15 minutes I played with this.  Some of the modules I didn\'t figure out how they worked.   I uninstall products that dont come with any instructions.  One star for a good subtraction module.
